{
  "id": null,
  "uid": "easymesh-qoe-usuario",
  "title": "EasyMesh - Observabilidad de Usuario y QoE",
  "tags": [
    "EasyMesh",
    "QoE",
    "usuario",
    "TelcoX",
    "TFG"
  ],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "5s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-30m",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "templating": {
    "list": []
  },
  "annotations": {
    "list": [
      {
        "builtIn": 1,
        "datasource": {
          "type": "grafana",
          "uid": "-- Grafana --"
        },
        "enable": true,
        "hide": true,
        "iconColor": "rgba(0, 211, 255, 1)",
        "name": "Annotations & Alerts",
        "type": "dashboard"
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "Cómo leer este dashboard",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "# Vista de usuario y QoE\n\nEste dashboard está pensado para enseñar **qué nota el usuario** cuando cambia el escenario del laboratorio.\n\n- **KPIs de usuario**: QoE, señal, latencia, pérdida, throughput y reintentos.\n- **Métricas TelcoX/TR-181**: señal, tasas de enlace, utilización y ruido de radio.\n- **KPIs derivados de laboratorio**: QoE, latencia y packet loss. Son útiles para explicar experiencia, pero no forman parte del perfil TelcoX estricto.\n"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {},
        "overrides": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Escenario activo",
      "type": "state-timeline",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 0,
            "fillOpacity": 70,
            "spanNulls": false
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              }
            ]
          },
          "mappings": []
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "mergeValues": true,
        "showValue": "always",
        "alignValue": "left",
        "rowHeight": 0.9,
        "legend": {
          "showLegend": true,
          "displayMode": "list",
          "placement": "bottom"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "single",
          "sort": "none"
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          },
          "expr": "easymesh_sim_scenario_info",
          "legendFormat": "{{scenario}} - {{description}}",
          "refId": "A",
          "range": true
        }
      ],
      "description": "Control de laboratorio. No es métrica TelcoX; sirve para correlacionar los cambios de escenario con las gráficas."
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "QoE media usuarios",
      "type": "gauge",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 8
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "orange",
                "value": 50
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 70
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 85
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "percent",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 100
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "values": false,
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": ""
        },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "showThresholdLabels": false,
        "showThresholdMarkers": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"
          },
          "expr": "avg(easymesh_sim_client_qoe_score)",
          "legendFormat": "QoE media",
          "refId": "A",
          "range": true
        }
      ],
      "description": "KPI derivado del laboratorio. Resume la experiencia de todos los clientes."
    },
